== 体育中的违禁用途 ==
利尿劑常被用于掩盖兴奋剂的存在，使药检不到，<ref>{{cite book |last=Bahrke |first=Michael |year=2002 |title=Performance-Enhancing Substances in Sport and Exercise |url= |deadurl= |location= |publisher= |isbn= |archiveurl= |archivedate= |accessdate= }}</ref>这是因为增加尿量可以稀释兴奋剂及其代谢物。还有一种违禁用途是快速減肥，以便在拳擊、摔跤等按重量分级的运动中满足某级要求。<ref>{{cite web |author=Agence France Presse |url=http://velonews.competitor.com/2012/07/news/uci-announces-positive-doping-test-for-frank-schleck-2_230302 |title=UCI announces adverse analytical finding for Frank Schleck |publisher=VeloNews |date=2012-07-17 |accessdate=2012-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120719081940/http://velonews.competitor.com/2012/07/news/uci-announces-positive-doping-test-for-frank-schleck-2_230302 |archive-date=2012-07-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2962812/ The abuse of diuretics as performance-enhancing drugs and masking agents in sport doping: pharmacology, toxicology and analysis] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2962812/ |date=20120719082730 }}, British Journal of Pharmacology, 2010-09.</ref>

